Fit propensity matrix for full model

FitOmega.Rd

(auxiliary function)

FitOmega(adj, xi, directed, selfloops)

Arguments

adj

adjacency matrix
xi

combinatorial matrix
directed

boolean
selfloops

boolean

Value

propensity matrix

Examples

data(adj_karate)
xi <- ComputeXi(adj_karate, FALSE, FALSE)
FitOmega(adj_karate, xi, FALSE, FALSE)
